        <b>{$tr('Be aware of scammers')}</b>{$tr(': please use only well-known markets to exchange XRT. Do not send your tokens to accounts given to you in private messages, regardless of the transaction type (buy or sell). If you receive any suspicious ‚Äúairdrops‚Äù or loud statements about Robonomics tokens, please verify updates on our')} <a
